{"tid":164933,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[成波之路]大阪豚平燒 (影片+圖文食譜)","createTime":"2017-03-21T04:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T05:44:49.000Z","uid":35319,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12452d88d201b6dc34e8209fad5a37ddf350f437","tid":164933,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"除咗大阪燒之外，大阪仲有獨有嘅「豚平燒」！<br />\n話就話係燒餅，其實無加粉漿，仲易整過大阪燒，最重要係可以用埋支大阪燒醬吖嘛！<br />\n影片：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/M60aZfebxuI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM60aZfebxuI&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6548b6e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/M60aZfebxuI</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:\t<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d5495ce2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nInstagram:\t<a href=\"http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ef3cb081\" target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nBlog:\t\t<a href=\"http://www.mywaystogetfat.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mywaystogetfat.com&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d56c7b2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mywaystogetfat.com</a><br />\n<strong>Blog 可以睇返之前出過post既食譜</strong><br />\n有興趣請like/follow/睇睇啦，多謝你既留意同支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4590755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4590755.jpg&h=7fdc2707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>份量：1 個豚平燒<br />\n<ins>材料</ins></strong>\t<br />\n青椰菜\t70 克<br />\n豬腩片\t70 克<br />\n鹽\t1/8 茶匙<br />\n雞蛋\t2 隻<br />\n砂糖\t1/2 茶匙<br />\n牛油溶液\t15 克<br />\n水\t1 湯匙<br />\n鰹魚素\t1/4 茶匙<br />\n大阪燒醬\t適量<br />\n日式蛋黃醬\t適量<br />\n海苔粉\t適量<br />\n柴魚片\t適量<br />\n<br />\n1. 把青椰菜切絲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/27T4701.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27T4701.jpg&h=a183b82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 把豬腩片切成方塊，兩面平均灑上鹽備用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/GRpc44U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRpc44U.jpg&h=745b6025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 把雞蛋、砂糖和牛油溶液拌勻備用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/6x49C66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6x49C66.jpg&h=476907d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 把水和鰹魚素拌勻備用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/2F022Xu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2F022Xu.jpg&h=a945a4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 以中大火燒熱鍋子，不用下油，下豬腩片煎兩面至出油。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/e94iyN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe94iyN5.jpg&h=be830846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 加入青椰菜炒 1 分鐘後，加入已拌勻的水和鰹魚素，多炒約 2 分鐘至豬肉熟透和椰菜變軟即成餡料，盛起備用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/9kdFi6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kdFi6z.jpg&h=6fdcc1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 抹淨鍋子後，以小火燒熱油，下蛋漿，以筷子攪拌約 30 秒。然後搖動鍋子讓蛋漿佈滿鍋底。煎至雞蛋半熟，即底部完全凝固，表面仍未熟的狀態。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/8QR2PW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QR2PW4.jpg&h=99f3f595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 把餡料平放在中間。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/ptoMO0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptoMO0z.jpg&h=70ae93bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 把雞蛋兩邊向內摺好壓實。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/9kj6pnU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kj6pnU.jpg&h=4aa879ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10. 用碟子一邊反轉蓋在鍋上，一邊翻轉鍋子上碟。依次掃上大阪燒醬、唧上日式蛋黃醬、灑上海苔粉和放上柴魚片即成。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/t1wMYzr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1wMYzr.jpg&h=715dc69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 可把適量牛奶加入日式蛋黃醬中，可以減輕蛋黃醬的味道，而且唧起來會比較順。"},{"pid":"9e90833a0ab0c78095210623e631d3f7c1ffb987","tid":164933,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4eca85ea41850d8468a82bb91bad4ffde02f618","tid":164933,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd51dc5b7e6fa7640d10759f70c7f04c9bc47791","tid":164933,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25addf5ba78b1c1fdc96ba852dd168d7dedab2e3","tid":164933,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5d48c73dfde650442ea570356fd94224904dd1","tid":164933,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咦唔係叫金正男㗎咩"},{"pid":"ab225ec2035ad224a3a6d48e5a70b6e1c1d09ed2","tid":164933,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3acc2dc13f888d48df4fb61bb9245eabe4ad3a8","tid":164933,"uid":26943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"aef1a619820248907cdabdcbdd5397974f