/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無秘方分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc7bcfc0201348ce793c15916aae2dbe59c9bd9","tid":164933,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生鐵鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日出埋啲咁感性嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呃下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你著返件底衫先啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f704b249b075f160ba70bd1f05b55299e020da","tid":164933,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本人正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767f354566414a0f1abaa936cace8eac78a53790","tid":164933,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T18:52:24.000Z","msg":"波波！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 波波你總共出過幾多本食譜呀？"}]}